Name: error indicator
Definition: Indicator that an item is in error.

Name: error rate
Definition: Number of the erroneous items with respect to the total number of items that should have been present.

Name: error count
Definition: Total number of items that are subject to an error of a specified type.

Name: correctness indicator
Definition: Indicator that an item is correct.

Name: correct items count
Definition: Total number of items that are free of errors of a specified type.

Name: correct items rate
Definition: Number of the correct items with respect to the total number of items that should have been present.
